    "C.3.1 Hardware DescriptionThe hardware demonstration was performed on two different superconducting quantum computers provided by IBM, with the smaller experiments performed on the 16-qubit ibmq guadalupe machine (see Fig. 15) and the larger ones on the 27-qubit ibm hanoi machine.",
